Twitter Coverage of Researcher@Library Week 2017

Peter Neish

2017-08-28 16:43:47

1 Introduction

An analysis of tweets from Researcher@Lbrary Week 2017. Code is available on GitHub.

289 tweets were collected using the rtweet R package:

rlweek <- search_tweets("#rlweek2017", 10000)
saveRDS(rlweek, "data/rlweek.rds")
